text.div:
PathologyTestResultStatusValues

Set of values for the pathology test result status.

This code system http://hl7.org/fhir/pathology-test-result-status-va defines the following codes:

Code Display Definition
1 Registered No result yet available.
2 Interim This is an initial or interim result: data may be missing or verification has not been performed.
3 Final The result is complete and verified by the responsible pathologist.
4 Amended The result has been modified subsequent to being Final, and is complete and verified by the responsible pathologist.
5 Cancelled/Aborted The result is unavailable because the test was not started or not completed.
